post.body:
Three quarters of the way through development for KopyKate v0.2.0..
&nbsp;
The navigation system is what took the longest amount of time to complete. Zite should be published by tonight.
&nbsp;
Quite a hassle really, but it will pay off in the long term. Coffeescript will make future coding faster, and jquery is easier to work with.  
