I should add. The **forward** button doesn't work with this code (even in the site example), and module.exports is undefined (why is there a node.js function?)
&nbsp;
It's also hard to come up with a routing system that deals with dynamically-generated Urls which contain video information, when this code defines routing anchors/urls with .add .. on site load.
&nbsp;
Then again, this code gave me lots of insights. I believe I'll be able to create a fully functional routing system by tomorrow. Nofish's routing on ZeroMe and ZeroUp is truly a piece of engineering.
&nbsp;
This is the only thing getting in the way of me re-creating KopyKate.
